description: Recording ID. Unique recording ID - a combination of media type, child ID, and month, e.g., video_41_12. See README or seedlings-nouns-codebook.csv for details.
Sub-recording start. Local time when the sub-recording started. The date for the first sub-recording of each recording was shifted to Jan 1, 1920 for anonymization purposes.
Sub-recording end. Local time when the sub-recording ended. See 'start'.
Sub-recording start position. Start of the sub-recording as the number of ms from the start of the audio file or the compiled video file.
